g.What are the ways to convert the string "123" into an integer and the list [1, 2, 3] into a
set? Demonstrate your approach.

#CONVERTING STRING INTO AN INTEGER

# Initialising a string
string = "123"

# Show the Data type
print(type(string))

# Converting string into int
string_to_int = int(string)

# Show the Data type
print(type(string_to_int))


